Longbow-CalledShot-Piercer-Dex-Standard
&{template:default} {{name=Ranged Attack - Longbow}} {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} fires an arrow at a target within range (150'/600').*}} [[ [[ [[1d8!cf<1cs>8 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[1d8!cf<0cs>11 [Called Shot]]] [Called Shot] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Dexterity_mod} [Dex]]] [Dex] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] + $[[1]] Piercing}} {{Dice Mods=$[[2]] varies}} {{Static=$[[4]] Piercing + $[[5]] Varies}} {{Dice Total=$[[3]] ***Dice Damage*** }} {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** }} {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** }} {{Piercer Feat= On a critical - deal an additional [[1d8cf<0cs>9]] Piercing damage}}
---------------------------------------------
